<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Statistics</title>
    <script
      type="text/javascript"
      src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-latest.min.js"
    ></script>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.1/css/all.min.css"
      integrity="sha512-KfkfwYDsLkIlwQp6LFnl8zNdLGxu9YAA1QvwINks4PhcElQSvqcyVLLD9aMhXd13uQjoXtEKNosOWaZqXgel0g=="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    />
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@3.8.0/dist/chart.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/statistics.css" />
    <script src="/js/statistics.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="flex-wrapper"><div class="content">
        <nav class="nav">
          <div class="select">
            <a
              href="#"
              class="link color-main dropdown-toggle"
              id="navigation_2_dropdown_1"
              >Go to</a
            >
            <div class="dropdown-menu">
              <div><a href="/">Home 🏠</a></div>
              <%if(user.role == "teacher"){%>
                <div><a href="/analyse">Analyse 🔎</a></div>
                <%}else{%>
                <div><a href="/search">Search 📙</a></div>
                <%}%>
              <div><a href="/logout">Logout 🚪</a></div>
             
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="greetings">
            <h3>
              Hey
              <h3 id="userEmail"><%=user.email%></h2>
              <h3>, these are our tool's statistics 📈...</h3>
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="logo">
            <h2 style="text-align: center">DataScrap</h2>
          </div>
        </nav>

        <div class="wrapper">
          <section class="columns">
            <div class="column">
              <h2>Interactivity Type 🐢</h2>
              <p>
                The pie chart <b class="trigger">below</b> gives information
                about the <i>type of interactivity</i> of the analysed
                documents.
              </p>
              <div
                class="chart-container not-show"
                style="position: relative; height: 100%; width: 100%"
              >
                <canvas
                  id="InteractivityTypeChart"
                  width="200"
                  height="200"
                  aria-label="Hello ARIA World"
                  role="img"
                ></canvas>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="column">
              <h2>Interactivity Levels 🌡️</h2>
              <p>
                The bar chart <b class="trigger">below</b> gives information
                about the <i>levels of interactivity</i> of the analysed
                documents .<br /><br />
              </p>
              <div
                class="chart-container not-show"
                style="position: relative; height: 100%; width: 100%"
              >
                <canvas
                  id="InteractivityLevelChart"
                  width="200"
                  height="200"
                  aria-label="Hello ARIA World"
                  role="img"
                ></canvas>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="column">
              <h2>Semantic Density ⚖️</h2>
              <p>
                The bar chart <b class="trigger">below</b> gives information
                about the levels of <i>semantic density</i> of the analysed
                documents .<br /><br />
              </p>
              <div
                class="chart-container not-show"
                style="position: relative; height: 100%; width: 100%"
              >
                <canvas
                  id="semanticDensityChart"
                  width="200"
                  height="200"
                  aria-label="Hello ARIA World"
                  role="img"
                ></canvas>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="columns">
            <div class="column">
              <h2>Text Richness ✍️</h2>
              <p>
                The bar chart <b class="trigger">below</b> gives information
                about the levels of <i>text richness</i> of the analysed
                documents .<br /><br />
              </p>
              <div
                class="chart-container not-show"
                style="position: relative; height: 100%; width: 100%"
              >
                <canvas
                  id="textRichnessChart"
                  width="200"
                  height="200"
                  aria-label="Hello ARIA World"
                  role="img"
                ></canvas>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="column">
              <h2>Text Readability 📖</h2>
              <p>
                The bar chart <b class="trigger">below</b> gives information
                about the levels of <i>readability</i> of the analysed documents
                .<br /><br />
              </p>
              <div
                class="chart-container not-show"
                style="position: relative; height: 100%; width: 100%"
              >
                <canvas
                  id="textReadabilityChart"
                  width="200"
                  height="200"
                  aria-label="Hello ARIA World"
                  role="img"
                ></canvas>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="columns">
            <div class="column">
              <h2>Reading Time ⏱️</h2>
              <p>
                The line chart <b class="trigger">below</b> gives information
                about the <i>reading time</i> of the analysed documents.<br /><br />
              </p>
              <div
                class="chart-container not-show"
                style="position: relative; height: 100%; width: 100%"
              >
                <canvas
                  id="readingTimeChart"
                  width="200"
                  height="200"
                  aria-label="Hello ARIA World"
                  role="img"
                ></canvas>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <div><p>© 2022</p></div>
        <div>
          <p>Made by <b>ElxHadi</b> and <b>marwadengou</b></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
